itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T03:16:11.000Z","msg":"戇鳩仔<br />\n就係愈讀愈知共產根本係冇可能<br />\n愈讀愈睇得多中共既醜陋<br />\n<br />\n如果乜都唔撚知 成個文盲咁人云亦云<br />\n你仲有乜撚野用 去考曱甴留返比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad837475ea2db2a18a0e6429e7f0f7fcb5f6db07","tid":2344541,"uid":132896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afd6fe9ccd1fb8b844a8440c6e0e6988338aa005","tid":2344541,"uid":327593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94366e3b3c6b27759783c33f365ac2dea170c907","tid":2344541,"uid":16057,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"925c37067d45bfd4d35953163e3aaac75d3fb130","tid":2344541,"uid":327593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T01:10:41.000Z","msg":"咪班愛國不愛黨既大中華撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T01:29:57.000Z","msg":"你都on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果按你地邏輯 唔好話中史 世史都唔應該係香港讀"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T01:43:44.000Z","msg":"講中唔敢駁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n十個讀中史九個對古中國有種浪漫性幻想<br />\n反共不反中<br />\n事實上中國由古至今都係一個垃圾民族國家<br />\n有冇一個教中史既老師會夠膽咁樣教？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T03:20:59.000Z","msg":"戇撚鳩<br />\n<br />\n自己冇批判思考？<br />\n老師點教 自己一定100%照單全收？<br />\n<br />\n第二 古中國一早玩完左好耐<br />\n同而家中共中國係唔撚同<br />\n有冇腦諗野？<br />\n古中國同古羅馬古希臘古埃及一樣有各自可取既地方 各自文化傳承既地方 <br />\n你會唔會話因為現今意大利希臘埃及垃圾 而否定n年前既野？<br />\n屌你老母 引戰鳩up就認<br />\n唔好係度懶理性 企高地先入為主<br />\n而家講緊歷史"},{"pid":"b366783c86cb236c7443dfdf2e9c2a555ab9f6d1","tid":2344541,"uid":132896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac7ec33284859c1a41ce8c8170e558b41a548c74","tid":2344541,"uid":327593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d806bb45732b073c29b5155d1af96e2f7979b60","tid":2344541,"uid":16057,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afd6fe9ccd1fb8b844a8440c6e0e6988338aa005","tid":2344541,"uid":327593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-29